Description:
    Creates a new front-end web application using rcreate/gulp-starter.

Options:
    Sass or Less: Include Sass oder Less
    Bootstrap: Include Bootstrap or Bootstrap Sass if Sass is included

Example:
    yo gulp-starter

    This will create:
        gulpfile.js: Configuration for the task runner.
        package.json: Development packages installed by npm.

        src/: Your application files.
        loaders/: Loaders for webpack
